main.java.sorter

Class TimeHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • main.java.sorter.TimeHandler

  • public class TimeHandler
extends java.lang.Object
    A class of static methods used for calculating the difference between two different entered times and sorting lists of times. The format used for times is hh.mm.ss .
    Author:
    team03
